1-07T01:54:04.000Z","msg":"自溫兆倫主力在大陸發展後，其微博變成了他的「愛國陣營」，天天發表「愛國正向思考」，歌頌「祖國」的美好和繁榮，2013年10月下旬，他發表了這樣的微博：「我的父母早逝，現在的我沒有爸沒媽但是我不怕；因為我還有我的國家，中國！不管我生在那裡？死在何處？我都是一個中國人！」<br />\n<br />\n接著他又表達了慶幸香港回歸中國的實現，令他成為一個有國家的人：「一個不愛國的人你也別奢望他會為別人或者社會付出有多大，因為他們最愛的是自己。我很慶倖97香港回歸到祖國的懷抱，我這個香港人在97年前是一個沒有國家的人，現在我很驕傲地說：我的國家中國，我是一個有血有肉的中國人！ 不管你們如何批評我都改變不了我愛祖國的心！」"},{"pid":"662982374f088492597eb51b8f833ea775fbcc26","tid":521583,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T02:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/07/105507_154c1c2560c20fbad112495cfa1c3ee0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F105507_154c1c2560c20fbad112495cfa1c3ee0.png&h=1a42cf5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對唔住</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc64a7c118508b6a4cc9bf7f313fd40ba5e7348","tid":521583,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c36a939bd91f86fda62eabd202016d4c76af2014","tid":521583,"uid":146621,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:55:54.000Z","msg":"做自己啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T02:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4f84528b3d5f56dd8b95d7e677ea717d6462c5","tid":521583,"uid":103218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T08:06:14.000Z","msg":"今晚重播我本善良"},{"pid":"1bb7137c0d55391d64b130b00ab38c10c97bfa34","tid":521583,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T08:09:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/07/105507_154c1c2560c20fbad112495cfa1c3ee0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F105507_154c1c2560c2